It is a busy year for arboviruses. It is a sad year for horse owners. Vaccination is critical and yet still many do not vaccinate their animals. Effective vaccines are available. Generally WNV is combined with eastern and western equine encephalitis and tetanus. This is a lot of protection for your horse for a small investment, but a large investment of time, money, love, and effort if you haven't vaccinated; please do so. - Mod.TG]
